Please help to improve this article by introducing more precise citations. *(February 2017)* *(Learn how and when to remove this message)* **Nadine Joy Nathan** (born 29 December 1999) is a Singaporean female [artistic gymnast](/wiki/Artistic_gymnast), representing her nation at international competitions. She competed at world championships, including the [2014 Youth Olympic Games](/wiki/2014_Youth_Olympic_Games), and the [2015 World Artistic Gymnastics Championships](/wiki/2015_World_Artistic_Gymnastics_Championships) in Glasgow. - "NATHAN Nadine Joy". *Database.fig-gymnastics.com*.
